I guess so… but think about it. I would wanna hit more frequently because even if you had 80 str and 1 attack, you will still get pwned by sum1 with 20 att and 75 str. Reason is that you might be able to hit a good load of damage, but it will only happen once every 2-5 hits… while a guy with 20 att and 75 str will hit a good load of damage on you every 1-3 hits.
